  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will contribute to fight against blindness in the Dominican Republic and improve the visual health of its inhabitants, especially those living in poverty in La Altagracia province, through the creation of an ophthalmological center in the community of Veron that will benefit to more than 273,000 inhabitants, thanks to the alliance with Fundacion Incivi, which has been partnering with Fundacion Grupo Puntacana for the last 6 years in the Ophthalmologic Mission Trips Project</narrative>
